are you doing here?

00:19:51.526 --> 00:19:52.794 position:16% line:89% align:start
I wanted to talk to you,

00:19:52.927 --> 00:19:54.428 position:24% line:83% align:start
because I wondered
what you meant before

00:19:54.562 --> 00:19:56.363 position:24% line:83% align:start
