00:19:58.298 --> 00:19:59.634 position:27% line:89% align:start
Isn't it obvious?

00:20:00.400 --> 00:20:02.136 position:21% line:83% align:start
It's 'cause Revozeale
is the best!

00:20:02.269 --> 00:20:04.271 position:24% line:83% align:start
She's the only hero
that I like!

00:20:05.238 --> 00:20:06.507 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm?

00:20:06.641 --> 00:20:08.308 position:13% line:83% align:start
And you've been pretending
to be her all day

00:20:08.442 --> 00:20:10.978 position:33% line:83% align:start
so that means
you're nothing but a faker!

00:20:11.344 --> 00:20:13.881 position:44% line:83% align:start
Wait.
Do you actually like Zeale?

00:20:14.015 --> 00:20:15.516 position:27% line:89% align:start
So what? Are you,

00:20:15.650 --> 00:20:17.417 position:10% line:89% align:start
gonna tell me that it's weird

00:20:17.552 --> 00:20:19.754 position:27% line:83% align:start
to like Civirevo
because I'm a boy?

00:20:20.088 --> 00:20:21.488 position:7% line:89% align:start
What's it matter if I like it?

00:20:21.789 --> 00:20:22.824 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jerk!

00:20:23.057 --> 00:20:24.592 position:38% line:83% align:start
-A jerk?
-Aah!

00:20:28.196 --> 00:20:30.631 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh! My Revozeale balloon!

00:20:32.033 --> 00:20:33.266 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:20:37.437 --> 00:20:39.339 position:38% line:89% align:start
Ah! Here.

00:20:40.742 --> 00:20:41.943 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
While it's not good to get

00:20:42.076 --> 00:20:43.544 position:10% line:89% align:start
too obsessed with something.

00:20:43.678 --> 00:20:46.047 position:19% line:83% align:start
Being able to shout to
the world about what you like,

00:20:46.647 --> 00:20:48.315 position:7% line:89% align:start
I think that's really amazing!

00:20:48.482 --> 00:20:49.483 position:33% line:89% align:start
I admire you!

00:20:49.617 --> 00:20:50.685 position:19% line:89% align:start
[MALE ZEALE FAN gasps]

00:20:50.952 --> 00:20:53.154 position:30% line:83% align:start
You know what?
If you like something.

00:20:53.487 --> 00:20:56.858 position:7% line:83% align:start
I don't think it really matters
what gender you happen to be.

00:20:57.225 --> 00:20:59.026 position:13% line:89% align:start
Wait, that sounds familiar!

00:20:59.392 --> 00:21:00.628 position:19% line:89% align:start
[MALE ZEALE FAN laughs]

00:21:00.995 --> 00:21:02.329 position:19% line:89% align:start
"If you like something,

00:21:02.462 --> 00:21:04.098 position:27% line:83% align:start
it doesn't matter
what gender you happen to be."

00:21:04.832 --> 00:21:07.902 position:7% line:83% align:start
That's exactly what Zeale said
in episode twenty-five!

00:21:09.504 --> 00:21:11.304 position:7% line:89% align:start
You-- you're real, aren't you?

00:21:11.606 --> 00:21:13.174 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're the real Revozeale!

00:21:13.373 --> 00:21:14.542 position:27% line:89% align:start
What do you mean?

00:21:14.709 --> 00:21:17.745 position:7% line:89% align:start
I-I'm not Revozeale! I-I'm Shy!

00:21:17.879 --> 00:21:19.647 position:27% line:83% align:start
[MALE ZEALE FAN]
I can't believe Zeale is here!

00:21:19.781 --> 00:21:22.550 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
I'm not Zeale!

00:21:24.685 --> 00:21:26.587 position:38% line:83% align:start
[exhales]
I don't know why,

00:21:26.721 --> 00:21:29.056 position:24% line:89% align:start
but I'm exhausted.

00:21:30.191 --> 00:21:33.594 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey! Thank you so much
for helping out! For real!

00:21:34.729 --> 00:21:37.464 position:13% line:83% align:start
It isn't much, but I've got
a little surprise for you!

00:21:37.932 --> 00:21:39.466 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
Oh, right! My reward!

00:21:39.667 --> 00:21:42.369 position:35% line:83% align:start
Aw, thanks!
But you really didn't have to--

00:21:42.837 --> 00:21:45.106 position:27% line:83% align:start
I present to you
the entire Civirevo

00:21:45.239 --> 00:21:46.874 position:27% line:83% align:start
30th anniversary
special edition

00:21:47.008 --> 00:21:48.408 position:27% line:89% align:start
Blu-ray box sets!

00:21:50.111 --> 00:21:51.145 position:44% line:89% align:start
Wow.

00:21:51.478 --> 00:21:52.713 position:44% line:83% align:start
[SHY]
Thanks a lot.

00:21:57.450 --> 00:21:58.653 position:35% line:83% align:start
[REVOZEALE]
Wake up, Revoron!

00:21:59.020 --> 00:22:01.155 position:13% line:83% align:start
