00:22:02.623 --> 00:22:04.491 position:27% line:89% align:start
Revoron? Revoron!

00:22:04.859 --> 00:22:06.527 position:21% line:83% align:start
[REVOZEALE] Revoron!
[SHY] Revoron!

00:22:06.894 --> 00:22:09.329 position:16% line:83% align:start
